<br>
Why not put in buyable wands, that would be lore and no drop, Wizards only.  These Wands could have either different prices for different spells or one large price and you could put say 5 of any one spell onto the wand.  To charge the wand, you target yourself and cast the spell.  One charge for each casting.  The wand would have a lesser casting time than the spell itself since the time and mana was used to charge the wand in the first place.  Upon zoneing the Charges are lost.  This would give wizards some extra firepower in big fights, but at the cost of mana and regen time, they would have to pick and choose what targets to use the wands on as it would take time and mana to recharge them.  It would also not increase thier ability to solo greatly, as it would take them time to charge the wand in the first place.<br>
<br>
<br>
Well I am sure there is something I forgot to put in that, but hey I am tired so feel free to tear me apart, and or post how you think it should be changed.<br>
<br>
Glina Fyreheart<br>
