<br>
Heck, you could even take it a step further and make it a component based craft similar to Alchemy.  Creation and sale of items with charges of spells in them.  Similar to gate potions, they could be sold to anyone, and used by anyone.  Call it Lorecraft or Arcane Creation or something.<br>
<br>
I would enjoy something like this simply because it creates a money making option that could be for wizards alone.<br>
<br>
Heck, lets create an Elemental Amulet for those few &quot;strange&quot; wizards who REALLY REALLY want pets...  lol<br>
